    "For instance, Sebastian et al. [102] and Zheng et al.",
    "[110] utilized the device-to-device variation in MoS 2 -based memtransistors to develop a random number generator and construct a Bayesian network for applications where uncertainty plays a crucial role.",
    "Furthermore, Chien et al.",
